	"system": {
		"description": "<p>Starting at <strong>1st level</strong>, your artifact inspires those who witness your exploits. Whenever you spend artifact charges to cast a wielder spell or exertion points on a maneuver, your bonded artifact inspires you and each allied creature within 15 feet until the start of your next turn. Creatures inspired in this way gain an expertise die on the next attack roll, check, or saving throw they make before the start of your next turn.</p><p>You can inspire creatures in this way a number of times equal to your proficiency bonus, any expended uses are regained when finishing a short or long rest.</p>",
